snippet.title: House of Necrosis - Survive the horrors of the mansion that changes every time you enter!
snippet.description:
Download the demo on itch.io https://warrrkus.itch.io/house-of-necrosis-demo?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Survive the horrors of the mansion that changes every time you enter.

House of Necrosis is a Mystery Dungeon-style game inspired by Survival Horror and RPG classics of the 32bit era.
